{"tid":324760,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個做過最最最後悔既事","createTime":"2017-07-16T16:14:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T06:19:46.000Z","uid":12458,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"05fa707daad5fd61aa7256d1ed947be88ba0a82f","tid":324760,"uid":12458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T16:14:24.000Z","msg":"細個10歲果陣經常返到學校都吐口水落同學個書包 基本上日日都最少3督左右 過左成個月 同學換左新書包 我問佢點解 佢話唔知點解好大陣口水臭味 我仲扮哂野話佢可能訓教果時流到 。有次上完pe堂我一野嘔落去佢個新書包到 佢喊完就無怪過我了 我仲記得佢坐我前面成日借文具比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我真係好後悔 李同學 我對你唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0249f53eb290bf0c05b7cdd357adee47c6d0e21","tid":324760,"uid":125780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T16:17:26.000Z","msg":"對個男仔講錯野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b726273439d36349bf18e7d92d7bf183ee7e39f8","tid":324760,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T16:26:36.000Z","msg":"有次去沙灘掉石仔<br />\n太大力掉咗上去<br />\n跌咗落個印印定唔知賓賓背脊<br />\n應該都幾傷下<br />\n對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eedaae20f20bf1645f337da8a1310fa7b001f1fc","tid":324760,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T16:28:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"500a20b61b96fa314caca7946849aa0fa7cded02","tid":324760,"uid":39971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T23:32:48.000Z","msg":"當時唔識處理一段關係 傷咗佢<img src=\"/assets/face